items.badge_description: It's New Brew Thursday! Drink any beer you have never had before on three different Thursdays in a 20 day period.

Looking for more kick than a session beer, but want to be able to stay for a few rounds? You have to keep it in the middle. That's 165 beers with an ABV greater than 5% and less than 10%. Try 5 more for Level 34!
It takes the perfect amount of light, the right framing and a touch of creative love to get the perfect picture of your brew. Now it’s time to drink it! That’s 120 check-ins with a photo.

Fresh from the tap is one of the best ways to enjoy a beer. Just try to use a glass and not drink directly from the tap, as tempting as it may be. That's 210 checkins with the serving style of Draft. Try 5 more for Level 43!

items.checkin_comment: Kinda west coast darker colour. Not bad.
